---
title: Spicy Veggie 'Jambalaya' Bowls with Beyond Meat® and Spicy Mayo
description: This veggie 'jambalaya' is wholesome, bursting with flavour and packed with protein from both kidney beans and Beyond Meat®.  The veggies and protein are simmered in a tomato-based sauce before being draped over basmati rice and finished off with a creamy kick from spicy mayo.
